[00:30.404]When I was young and lost
[00:37.212]You showed up, and had my doors unlocked
[00:44.942]Like threads, petals unfold
[00:51.267]A red kawara-nadeshiko
[00:56.868]
[00:59.056]You have shown me that I am still capable of caring for someone else
[01:13.924]That I still bare the same innocence inside
[01:26.044]
[01:26.667]Cause now I know that
[01:29.050]Pain cannot define the past
[01:32.114]We are built to overcome endless mishaps
[01:37.081]You know, it is not so bad
[01:41.323]When you are with me
[01:43.485]Cherish as long as we last
[01:46.686]Cause S is not for sayonara
[01:52.188]Let memories play back
[01:56.330]
[02:23.208]I knew I must step up
[02:29.842]You deserve the world and more
[02:37.569]The truth is that you'd rather
[02:43.977]Spend our limited time together
[02:51.249]
[02:51.752]Protection alone is not enough
[02:59.528]Providing cannot fill an empty cup thirsting for love
[03:10.342]I questioned myself a lot–
[03:18.854]
[03:43.493]What do I know about love?
[03:46.686]How can I recreate what I've never had?
[03:51.651]All I know is that I must keep you thriving
[03:58.137]If nutrients are what you lack
[04:01.085]I will water you with every drop of blood I have
[04:09.876]
[04:10.336]But now I know that
[04:12.685]Sacrifice is the easy path
[04:15.860]My absence cannot ever change the fact
[04:20.522]I wanted the very best for you, believe me
[04:26.906]Our threads in red can never be cut
[04:30.418]And S is not for sayonara
[04:35.868]Will you forgive me at last?
